  "description": "<p><strong>感谢<a href=\"http://www.coolxap.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WP8</a>的投递</strong><br /></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 0px;\">﻿</span><strong>最近随着“钢铁超人”电影的发布，诺基亚围绕着该电影做了大量的宣传。从预告片中的内容以及“拯救黑暗世界”的主题可以看出，诺基亚宣传的是Lumia925的低光拍摄能力。</strong>诺基亚最近的宣传广告一直重点推广的拍照技术，从lumia920的防抖技术，Lumia928的疝气闪光灯，Lumia925的低光拍摄功能，到即将发 布的4100万像素的Lumia EOS，诺基亚在拍照技术上费了很大的功夫，也希望这个特色的功能能够得到用户的认可。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2db06c5f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242222.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%BA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%3A%E6%90%BA%E6%89%8B%E9%92%A2%E9%93%81%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%AF%E6%95%91%E9%BB%91%E6%9A%97%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242222.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%BA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%3A%E6%90%BA%E6%89%8B%E9%92%A2%E9%93%81%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%AF%E6%95%91%E9%BB%91%E6%9A%97%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242222.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%BA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%3A%E6%90%BA%E6%89%8B%E9%92%A2%E9%93%81%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%AF%E6%95%91%E9%BB%91%E6%9A%97%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242222.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%BA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%3A%E6%90%BA%E6%89%8B%E9%92%A2%E9%93%81%E