  "description": "<p><strong>垃圾短信一直是社会的“顽疴”。媒体不断曝光，用户不断投诉，运营商不断打击，但是垃圾短信现象不但没有得到根治，反而有愈演愈烈之趋势。垃圾短信治理，要害在哪里？</strong>含有“发票”、“培训”字眼的短信就一定是垃圾短信吗？封堵垃圾短信，到底哪些部门说了算？国外有没有垃圾短信，他们是怎么管理的？带着疑虑和困惑，下面的故事或许可以解答不少人的疑问。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2db06c5b/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242221.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%9F%AD%E4%BF%A1%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B+%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%9A%BE%E7%A6%81%E9%9A%BE%E7%BB%9D%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242221.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%9F%AD%E4%BF%A1%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B+%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%9A%BE%E7%A6%81%E9%9A%BE%E7%BB%9D%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242221.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%9F%AD%E4%BF%A1%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B+%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%9A%BE%E7%A6%81%E9%9A%BE%E7%BB%9D%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242221.htm&amp;t=%E8%AF%B4%E8%AF%B4%E4%BD%A0%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%9F%AD%E4%BF%A1%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B+%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%9A%BE%E7%A6%81%E9%9A%BE%E7%BB%9D%EF%BC%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feeds