  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242220.htm", 
  "description": "<p>以前，虚拟现实头盔的视野都很有限，感觉就像坐在黑屋子里看一台放在几米外的电视。但Oculus Rift却把你放到屏幕里面，图像可以充满你的整个视野。还融合了立体声3D技术，实现了无可匹敌的沉浸感。<strong>美国科技博客BusinessInsider今天撰文称，Oculus Rift虚拟现实头盔可以打消人们对虚拟现实游戏的一切顾虑，提供的效果十分理想，甚至连很多普通消费者都迫不及待地购买开发者版。</strong><br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2db06c59/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242220.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5DOculus%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E5%A4%B4%E7%9B%94%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242220.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5DOculus%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E5%A4%B4%E7%9B%94%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242220.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5DOculus%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E5%A4%B4%E7%9B%94%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242220.htm&amp;t=%5B%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%5DOculus%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E5%A4%B4%E7%9B%94%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.fe